專任教師



管希聖
             助 理教 授 
            1999 年 美國馬里蘭大學 博士
            電話：(02)3366-5163
          Email：goan@phys.ntu.edu.tw 


教學與研究領域 :
研究領域： 
              1.凝態物理理論 2.介觀與奈米物理理論 
              3.固態量子計算理論 
              4.量子測量理論 
              5.單電荷與單自旋的測量理論 
            6.量子(奈米)電力學系統 

              教學： 
以量子計算與資訊導論, 凝(固)態物理理論,以及介觀物理理論為主 


Selected Publications

              (1)? H.-S. Goan, G. J. Milburn, H. M. Wiseman, and H. B. Sun, “ Continuous quantum measurement of two coupled quantum dots using a point contact: A quantum trajectory approach ”, Phys. Rev. B 63 , 125326 (2001). 
(2)? H.-S. Goan and G. J. Milburn, “Dynamics of a mesoscopic charge quantum bit under continuous quantum measurement”, Phys. Rev. B 64 , 235307 (2001). 
(3)? H.-S. Goan, “ An analysis of reading out the state of a charge quantum bit ”, Quantum Information and Computation 3 , 121 (2003). 
(4)? C. D. Hill and H.-S. Goan, “Fast non-adiabatic two-qubit gates for the Kane quantum computer”, Phys. Rev. A 68 , 012321 (2003). 
(5)? L. M. Kettle, H.-S. Goan, S. C. Smith, C. J. Wellard, L.C.L. Hollenberg and C.I. Pakes, “ A numerical study of hydrogenic effective mass theory for an impurity P donor in Si in the presence of an electric field and interfaces ”, Phys. Rev. B 68 , 075317 (2003). 
(6)? T. A. Brun and H.-S. Goan, “ Realistic simulations of single-spin nondemolition measurement by magnetic resonance force microscopy ”, Phys. Rev. A 68 , 032301 (2003). 
(7)? D. W. Utami, H.-S. Goan and G. J. Milburn, “ Charge transport in a quantum electromechanical system ”, Phy. Rev. B 70 , 075303 (2004). 
(8)? H.-S. Goan, “ Monte Carlo method for a quantum measurement process by a single-electron transistor ”, Phys. Rev. B 70 , 075305 (2004). 
(9)? D. H. Santamore, H.-S. Goan, G. J. Milburn and M. L. Roukes, “ Anharmonic effects on a phonon number measurement of a quantum mesoscopic mechanical oscillator ”, Phys. Rev. A 70 , 052105 (2004). 
(10)? T. M. Stace, S.D. Barrett, H.-S. Goan and G. J. Milburn, “ Parity measurement of one- and two-electron double well systems ”, Phys. Rev. B 70 , 205342 (2004). 
?


 






